    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes a basic set of fundamental mechanisms for
routing on a Low-power and Lossy Network (LLN).  It does not intend
to specify a full-blown protocol.  It is rather offered as a basis to
support the discussion while designing the ROLL protocol.</t>
